bio: Aimée Kennedy is the designer and creator of the well known fashion jewellery label “Fine and Good”. It has been a favourite of celebrities, stylists and the media since 2003. This popular line is stylish, trendy, funky and is fun and easy to wear. Classically trained as a sculptor and with over 10 years experience as a graphic designer, Aimée is uniquely suited to design jewellery. She has explored many different specialized jewellery techniques including glass flame-working, traditional enamel and metal fusing. She is also an accomplished bespoke fine jewellery designer using CAD technology as well as traditional methods to create custom jewellery and wedding and engagements rings.
